oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: I Guess I'll Go On Dreaming - Wilburn Brothers performance - KWKH ; I've Just Told Mama Goodbye - Wilburn Brothers performance - KWKH
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of I Guess I'll Go On Dreaming, written by Johnnie Bailes, Walter Bailes, Zeke Clements, and Muriel Deason Wright, and performed by the Wilburn Brothers. Performance of I Just Told Mama Goodbye, written by Curley Kinsey and Slim Sweet, and performed by the Wilburn Brothers. Both performances were on the Wilburn Brother's radio program on KWKH (Shreveport, La.).
